metadata.name: Woman of Fire
metadata.description:
"As I walk down the hallway, I see a woman with red hair ahead of me. She stops and turns around to look at me."
- Metaverse Dreams

"I see that she has a huge grin on her face and she is waving to me. She says, "Hey! I see you!" I can't help but smile back at her."
- Generated by AI

~

Made with a combination of VQGAN, CLIP, GPT-J, and Disco Diffusion models.
